sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OMC as odh-model-controller<br/>Operator
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NVCR as nvcr.io Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Client as Dashboard / CLI
    participant MSA as model-serving-api<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,OMC: Flow 1: InferenceService Reconciliation
    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService
    K8sAPI->>OMC: Watch event (HTTPS/6443)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    OMC->>K8sAPI: Create Route (HTTPS/6443)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    OMC->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy (HTTPS/6443)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    OMC->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor (HTTPS/6443)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    OMC->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding (HTTPS/6443)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over User,OMC: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService AuthPolicy
    User->>K8sAPI: Create LLMInferenceService
    K8sAPI->>OMC: Watch event (HTTPS/6443)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    OMC->>K8sAPI: Read LLMInferenceServiceConfig<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    OMC->>K8sAPI: Create/Update AuthPolicy<br/>targeting HTTPRoute<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over User,OMC: Flow 3: Gateway EnvoyFilter + AuthPolicy
    User->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Gateway
    K8sAPI->>OMC: Watch event (HTTPS/6443)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    OMC->>K8sAPI: Check Authorino TLS status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    OMC->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter<br/>(TLS bootstrap)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    OMC->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy<br/>targeting Gateway<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over OMC,NVCR: Flow 4: NIM Account Validation
    K8sAPI->>OMC: Watch NIM Account event<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    OMC->>NGC: Validate API key<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (NGC key)
    NGC-->>OMC: API key valid + catalog data
    OMC->>NVCR: Validate registry access<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (registry token)
    NVCR-->>OMC: Token exchange success
    OMC->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (model catalog)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    OMC->>K8sAPI: Create Secret (pull secret)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    OMC->>K8sAPI: Create Template (NIM ServingRuntime)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over Client,MSA: Flow 5: Gateway Discovery API
    Client->>MSA: GET /api/v1/gateways?namespace=X<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+ FIPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (user's K8s token)
    MSA->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>Auth: User's Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>MSA: Access granted
    MSA->>K8sAPI: List Gateways<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>MSA: Gateway list
    MSA-->>Client: JSON: filtered Gateways<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
